---
title: Super Quick Bulgogi Beef with Sugar Snaps, Jasmine Rice and Peanuts
description: Ready in just 15 minutes, our Super Quick Bulgogi Beef is sticky and fully delicious. Layers of flavour are built through Korean favourite bulgogi, mango chutney, soy and Indonesian spices.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R08_W39_UK_UQ16496-4_Main__4low-badc3838.jpg
